name: Alice in Neverland Skeleton Key Tribal Fusion Necklace
description:
In the future Alice will travel to a new land called Neverland, which rivals the bizarre and wonderful adventures she's had in her comparably quaint trip down the rabbit hole. Travel far beyond the looking glass with this steampunk siren necklace, dripping with all the Bedouin enchantment of the most beautiful member of the king's harem, plus a generous dash of mischief and adventure.

Made from a montage of mesmerizing tribal metal charms and pendants and accented with a collection of little skeleton keys, this necklace is the ultimate in tribal steampunk luxury! Necklace measures about 18" around and central crescent pendant measures about 3.5" wide and 6" long. Features an easy on-and-off clasp that can adjust for the perfect length. description:
